By":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:58:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多圖=1張<br />\n有圖=0張<br />\n無圖=好多張"},{"pid":"e19249e9008b2664ecb95770776fb5f49f30c934","tid":28640,"uid":3358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:59:33.000Z","msg":"唔明你地做咩咁反感<br />\n可能係個小朋友自己想做呢<br />\n我讀書個時都好鐘意做功課<br />\n又唔係個家長逼佢<br />\n完全唔覺得有問題"},{"pid":"6909c92406c41bbe4c70c5c0ff4935f92c8ca5ca","tid":28640,"uid":22323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:00:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起細個果陣默書唔合格<br />\n去到最報一刻就落車先敢俾呀媽簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小學功課一直都好多<br />\n寫到手冊都唔夠位記低但個老師都仲要繼續俾<br />\n戇鳩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你幾歲<br />\n我以前小學真係無乜功課做<br />\n下午校每日6點點放學，一個鐘點都做哂d野<br />\n第朝就睇至net小人類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90490c866c87ae806e01492d82776d7d365b8389","tid":28640,"uid":22301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:00:40.000Z","msg":"入到大學仲有排受，mid term, proj , final<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6922fa4dee21a68fe03f353cbc9b74cd78e65468","tid":28640,"uid":22323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:01:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔明你地做咩咁反感<br />\n可能係個小朋友自己想做呢<br />\n我讀書個時都好鐘意做功課<br />\n又唔係個家長逼佢<br />\n完全唔覺得有問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我意思係宜家小學好似多功課過我果時姐"},{"pid":"67aceadcebbf0a2ac21d753a2ce47faeb3de9536","tid":28640,"uid":19157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:04:57.000Z","msg":"以前都見過同學咁做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過好慘 就算係車做哂d功課 返到去都仲要溫書"},{"pid":"5596a6f52bfbc59d13c4eea81b5dd0bca86abd13","tid":28640,"uid":51204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:05:06.000Z","msg":"果日搭巴士上層見到個小學生係度抄緊詞語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個老母仲坐係隔離"},{"pid":"3c44e4322255cc0ba7d605e05bbc9706e5f8d581","tid":28640,"uid":22323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:06:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>果日搭巴士上層見到個小學生係度抄緊詞語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個老母仲坐係隔離</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n照抄既功課真心唔明有乜撚野用，on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0743266e064a44169e1ed2fdafd19152367baf81","tid":28640,"uid":51204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:06:38.000Z","msg":"諗返起我果陣放學去補個半鐘習就做哂啲功課喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 返屋企係玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申屋邨小學年年考第一"},{"pid":"edb3556fe4f4080aba33f6c612fb47be6b169594","tid":28640,"uid":15639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:07:31.000Z","msg":"當一切都進步緊，唯獨教育仲停留"},{"pid":"aeb00f0c16d0fb8af8d555715dad6fc329b7bf5d","tid":28640,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:08:46.000Z","msg":"人生80年，依家啲小朋友懂性開始就要食屎食到死果日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c88d9f0bf7e81fc9f02409e9b5ca729a4e2ec0","tid":28640,"uid":27612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:08:52.000Z","msg":"其實老師都唔想俾功課，你估真係唔洗改咩？<br />\n宜家啲學生唔係語文有問題，係邏輯有問題，當你對住30篇完全冇邏輯可言既英文作文，真係唔知可以點改&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n最on9就係個校長，不停咁叫老師俾功課！啲學生識做先得架！practice not necessarily makes perfect！啲學生根本唔明，只係不停咁做做做，校長就只顧學校排名，根本唔係以學生為本！"},{"pid":"e9553425cf17c9fdfa3ed2518703b9013c59363d","tid":28640,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:12:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>多圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多圖=1張<br />\n有圖=0張<br />\n無圖=好多張</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n激多圖 = 3至4張圖<br />\n多圖 = 1張圖<br />\n有圖 = 無圖<br />\n冇圖 = 屌你老母真係冇圖"},{"pid":"8ebc0b26c08c365682c11f11924489f2fa2aefbb","tid":28640,"uid":33729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:15:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔明你地做咩咁反感<br />\n可能係個小朋友自己想做呢<br />\n我讀書個時都好鐘意做功課<br />\n又唔係個家長逼佢<br />\n完全唔覺得有問題</blockquote><br />\n呢句真，小學個時每日2,3樣，係周末先多d<br />\n大部份都係抄下課文詞語，差唔多一兩版就做晒，仲要好比心機寫到靚一靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb89ab25405e191b0caf239de1af0406c87abe8","tid":28640,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:15:54.000Z","msg":"因為我地呢代同上一代無幫佢地爭取過任何野"},{"pid":"58b0957ea568e4726b28778454e9d7ae4f9e31c3","tid":28640,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:22:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔明你地做咩咁反感<br />\n可能係個小朋友自己想做呢<br />\n我讀書個時都好鐘意做功課<br />\n又唔係個家長逼佢<br />\n完全唔覺得有問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鐘意做功課到要係車做已經係問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66f4bb7f9446c7e5305b3587bd80521f207b1480","tid":28640,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:25:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔明你地做咩咁反感<br />\n可能係個小朋友自己想做呢<br />\n我讀書個時都好鐘意做功課<br />\n又唔係個家長逼佢<br />\n完全唔覺得有問題</blockquote><br />\n呢句真，小學個時每日2,3樣，係周末先多d<br />\n大部份都係抄下課文詞語，差唔多一兩版就做晒，仲要好比心機寫到靚一靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前會有時間練書法<br />\n寫下毛筆字練字<br />\n而家我諗小學生連咩叫「臨摹」都唔知係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9eee9c531c28b79fce62711bd6ecee073d9572","tid":28640,"uid":33729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:26:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔明你地做咩咁反感<br />\n可能係個小朋友自己想做呢<br />\n我讀書個時都好鐘意做功課<br />\n又唔係個家長逼佢<br />\n完全唔覺得有問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鐘意做功課到要係車做已經係問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能人地諗住係車拿拿聲鳩做完，返歸咪可以訓覺打機打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8beee67b9978fa44facf1936abbb29b007e08c0","tid":28640,"uid":54812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:33:26.000Z","msg":"唔係不嬲都多咩？<br />\n我以前4，5年級已經日日十幾樣<br />\n中指有舊繭都係個時磨番尼"},{"pid":"8a1f42b849c81e731db8cf96f0b2681c43a2e3d8","tid":28640,"uid":10351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:35:38.000Z","msg":"多圖？"},{"pid":"f26f52e140adfae5c9aa0086aeef54d5eb9f14fe","tid":28640,"uid":16281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:37:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"adc8020b9237023c30479193eee929053a9d22a4","tid":28640,"uid":44933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:38:05.000Z","msg":"人地搭車做完返屋企睇電視咋"},{"pid":"9b7193249834dffc152539299855838c840fc4f9","tid":28640,"uid":27830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:41:32.000Z","msg":"細個搭校車都會做功課<br />\n返屋企唔洗做有得睇電視"},{"pid":"5cb872351abd6c17cb7a2d74e1c69e7340d8075c","tid":28640,"uid":50327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:47:30.000Z","msg":"細個成日偷偷地做定d 練習，有時間就做吓<br />\n老師開頭有屌, 之後都由得我<br />\n小五小六一返到屋企開飯枱用一兩個鐘做功課<br />\n其實只要夠專注，每日十零樣功課都唔係問題<br />\n我仲記得拿拿聲五點前做完睇卡通<br />\n而家啲細路最大問題係唔夠定，太多物質引誘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b6458841bdd649c52ac2993756dfb8c0b0d004","tid":28640,"uid":13845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:47:40.000Z","msg":"學校派完 之後補習班再派練習 屋企人屎忽痕行過書局再買本補充練習 之後仲要上課外活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時睇見個細姪女都覺得慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記得細個放學老母有時會帶我去公園玩陣，e架3 4點行過公園都好少見到小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9c8a2c02d517bbc13793bd006e55eb85afa614","tid":28640,"uid":32377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:53:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個成日偷偷地做定d 練習，有時間就做吓<br />\n老師開頭有屌, 之後都由得我<br />\n小五小六一返到屋企開飯枱用一兩個鐘做功課<br />\n其實只要夠專注，每日十零樣功課都唔係問題<br />\n我仲記得拿拿聲五點前做完睇卡通<br />\n而家啲細路最大問題係唔夠定，太多物質引誘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n+1，小息同中午食飯時間清咁幾份，返到屋企專心做就會快啲做完"},{"pid":"9222ac0fac8c451ec797d889f5566bde12b13689","tid":28640,"uid":31071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T07:00:19.000Z","msg":"唔交功課好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833fb9b90502991a7d73c27ed97a2cae078da424","tid":28640,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T07:16:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宜家啲學生一日十份功課係正常<br />\n仲會特登慢慢做到九點幾十點先走<br />\n因為早做完返到屋企都冇得玩<br />\n寧願喺補習社hea<br />\n見到都心up<br />\n<br />\n利申返社習社</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe7d56593710c247453fc8a64cc5a75d36e02410","tid":28640,"uid":46610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T07:26:45.000Z","msg":"小學係多功課架啦<br />\n不過多唔代表難做<br />\nd小學雞最鍾意數自己有幾撚多樣<br />\n簽名一份 改正一份 ws仔一份<br />\n其實睇佢有冇能力姐 <br />\n有能力根本好多做完<br />\n家長問題先係最大"},{"pid":"c9a19b02df4735c90edd044ebdc4faca23f75a97","tid":28640,"uid":23902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T07:27:41.000Z","msg":"係學生都慘架啦<br />\n利申升中3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ce40488a6b0239a3d226f9473982c2aab70a75","tid":28640,"uid":38784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T07:55:49.000Z","msg":"細個果陣 小學星期五通常都多d功課  之後都係星期日6點先開始做  細個已經係deadline fighter   宜家d小學生仲有冇依隻歌仔飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"545a3a39dab7347b0bf67c8b5e2ecec4d266c8b6","tid":28640,"uid":38784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T07:56:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個果陣 小學星期五通常都多d功課  之後都係星期日6點先開始做  細個已經係deadline fighter   宜家d小學生仲有冇依隻歌仔<span style=\"color: red;\">唱</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"81209890a0b856f46809195f8cad01a3ebdf4133","tid":28640,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:03:17.000Z","msg":"係香港有咩人唔慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d3b37164cc8cd58470b77e72ad07bd7efc5c2c","tid":28640,"uid":7026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:24:51.000Z","msg":"細個一日十七份功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c18838adfdc4e65eb9611f57b302da6d2e5370f","tid":28640,"uid":49918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:33:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5bf59db59195648a79f5a6ab36a772590f54614a","tid":28640,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:38:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個都勁多功課，記憶中好似日日最少五六樣，最多八九樣，唔計放假<br />\n<br />\n初時追得勁辛苦，晚晚做到10點幾11點，後尾去到一個點發現根本冇可能做晒，就開始放棄，番學校搵人借黎抄或者唔交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實細個最開心係沙士果段假期<br />\n老師俾唔徹功課就放長假<br />\n當然對於患者及逝去嘅病人深表同情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a88b93611b197d26b69fe6493f8d1c43a25ee2","tid":28640,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:43:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係不嬲都多咩？<br />\n我以前4，5年級已經日日十幾樣<br />\n中指有舊繭都係個時磨番尼</blockquote><br />\n我以前大約一日4～6樣左右咋<br />\n嗰陣仲未有全日制，下晝返屋企睇etv直落睇埋兒童時段嘅卡通，做功課，差唔多食飯嗰陣就做完，食完飯仲可以玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca7fabd7f77b9ecb0cabc671fe2a3ed07a7e1074","tid":28640,"uid":6106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:45:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係不嬲都多咩？<br />\n我以前4，5年級已經日日十幾樣<br />\n中指有舊繭都係個時磨番尼</blockquote><br />\n我以前大約一日4～6樣左右咋<br />\n嗰陣仲未有全日制，下晝返屋企睇etv直落睇埋兒童時段嘅卡通，做功課，差唔多食飯嗰陣就做完，食完飯仲可以玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加一 小學明明係on99輕輕鬆鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf09a1e06e5406c34320d30763ea7003719f9be","tid":28640,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:49:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係不嬲都多咩？<br />\n<br />\n我以前4，5年級已經日日十幾樣<br />\n<br />\n中指有舊繭都係個時磨番尼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我以前大約一日4～6樣左右咋<br />\n<br />\n嗰陣仲未有全日制，下晝返屋企睇etv直落睇埋兒童時段嘅卡通，做功課，差唔多食飯嗰陣就做完，食完飯仲可以玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加一 小學明明係on99輕輕鬆鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以你唔怪得而家啲中小學雞郁啲就跳樓，當你得幾歲返preschool開始就註定你跟住落嚟呢十幾年仲慘過返工，試問咁樣成長嘅人仲對將來可以有咩希望"},{"pid":"b5c25127b3b511b569b11e6136887db4c3773c74","tid":28640,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:53:31.000Z","msg":"以前小學每日功課4，5樣到<br />\n通常抄書個d會係學校小息個陣偷做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n之前見我外甥做功課做到夜晚12點幾都未做完<br />\n睇一睇手冊 嘩 十幾樣功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc616406b30033c09eece705a9db255cdc94e5b2","tid":28640,"uid":54597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:20:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔明你地做咩咁反感<br />\n可能係個小朋友自己想做呢<br />\n我讀書個時都好鐘意做功課<br />\n又唔係個家長逼佢<br />\n完全唔覺得有問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我意思係宜家小學好似多功課過我果時姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n肯定多好多"},{"pid":"485c4500c91f5342b6c155173e4c07d795c46885","tid":28640,"uid":46680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:31:50.000Z","msg":"點解係「以家」？<br />\n<br />\n當年已經係咁<br />\n<br />\n利申：198x"},{"pid":"8a2fb4159c552c7cea41b1aaec5c69bd3f9d3330","tid":28640,"uid":46680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:32:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>果日搭巴士上層見到個小學生係度抄緊詞語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個老母仲坐係隔離</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n照抄既功課真心唔明有乜撚野用，on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n練寫字囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5512b2ab0ea463af4a4451c3edd8d1fece3d17d","tid":28640,"uid":32586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:35:17.000Z","msg":"我當年都已經十鳩幾樣"},{"pid":"4fb9b67a1fa2c8f6ddbb13d8d9353ff35e327f2d","tid":28640,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:55:31.000Z","msg":"做完返屋企打機"},{"pid":"e97c781258236a1b99ee8cd8fac831018eecc7a3","tid":28640,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:57:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去等睇醫生做功課我都見過<br />\n痴撚線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1235094e93795712a4bbff1f51c04e068d266955","tid":28640,"uid":32676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:30:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>果日搭巴士上層見到個小學生係度抄緊詞語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個老母仲坐係隔離</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n照抄既功課真心唔明有乜撚野用，on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n練寫字囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n練咗十幾年，啲字仲係咁樣衰<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">咁當然要靚就實寫到嘅</span></span>"},{"pid":"37c1e5149badbe70ccb22a31b43e60bd37bf2a6e","tid":28640,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:17:40.000Z","msg":"小學d功課真係輕鬆應付<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰陣時平日係學校已經做哂，淨係長假期前十幾二十樣先搞唔哂，要返屋企做，都係兩個鐘左右"},{"pid":"2d62f1d8033fb582be94d470461c8286a58838fa","tid":28640,"uid":10837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:34:46.000Z","msg":"以前覺得係車度做功課呢啲係扮嘢<br />\n依家覺得佢哋好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c0a26e48cd5864580c154409cc7dc1ca31f3c51","tid":28640,"uid":16281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T13:27:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"93eed54b001c931dd5473c496ab0ad76c12d88a1","tid":28640,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T14:32:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e0d7959afa184107466c3a3705f418f266a1da","tid":28640,"uid":43804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T14:33:27.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 勁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9508171027005ea788b9731f40d1c235f656ef27","tid":28640,"uid":56725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T14:36:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91b3522f267f9c8933bed379013281591ae4b4dc","tid":28640,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T14:42:52.000Z","msg":"慘既唔係多功課<br />\n慘既係逼佢地做"},{"pid":"072858e7614cbcd080b8121bd5aa8a80c8178b8b","tid":28640,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T14:45:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab06a9b8489c52483971b355d0d25aa41dc3c23d","tid":28640,"uid":43358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T14:46:57.000Z","msg":"我細個咪又係咁"},{"pid":"2faec8358539bdb473d12cd0d1d5ccf216b212fd","tid":28640,"uid":30972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:16:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為我地呢代同上一代無幫佢地爭取過任何野</blockquote><br />\n你唔好亂講呀 我有罷交功課㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa669b886bbbd0a7d2ac55883a64e57e61f98dd","tid":28640,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:19:52.000Z","msg":"自己屋村小學大  依家係屋村小學教<br />\n功課係多 但啲細路好快做完  有啲痴線既小息做 放學做哂<br />\n問佢地放學有咩做 就係睇埋啲言情小說 打機 <br />\n其實同我細個差唔多　<br />\n見佢地又唔會話成日溫書咁<br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪因為屋村學校，屋企人無錢比佢地學依樣學果樣<br />\n但同依家傳媒講既真係兩回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdacf52b4c0b880d23820022c4b8ee721e7453d9","tid":28640,"uid":6851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:44:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宜家啲小學功課又煩又難<br />\n問班細路點解要慢慢磨到九點先走<br />\n佢哋話返到屋企都冇嘢做好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問佢哋有咩嘢想做<br />\n佢哋話冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽得岀已經係機器式冇哂意志<br />\n<br />\n利申補習社啱啱放工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽到都覺得慘<br />\n由小學開始就要做奴隸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7604db4dd32e92f6f7d30c2b5efe5edb1f9c74e6","tid":28640,"uid":13768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:46:14.000Z","msg":"德信小學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69df2f231dce73d8a520dc43647ae05a25bb1fae","tid":28640,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:47:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我當年都已經十鳩幾樣</blockquote><br />\n當年返半日, 仲有半日去做功課<br />\n家下D學生又全日制, 又可能有課餘活動, 夜晚先有得開始做功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"101863fbfe45a40441b2238c7002286e90788077","tid":28640,"uid":9805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:47:55.000Z","msg":"以前小學每日十鳩幾樣功課,每晚至少十二點先訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：九十後<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}